--- src/complexity.js ---
@sig ddd77195
calculateComplexity(body)→walk.simple|compute cyclomatic complexity from AST body
getRating(complexity)|return severity rating from complexity score
export analyzeComplexityFile(code,relPath)→parse,calculateComplexity,getRating,items.push,walk.simple|analyze complexity for all functions in a single file
export getComplexity(dir,options=)→resolve,findJSFiles,analyzeFile,allItems.push,allItems.filter,allItems.sort|scan directory, filter and sort complexity results
PATTERNS: AST tree walking via Acorn|cyclomatic complexity counting
EDGE_CASES: parses arrow functions with blocks|ignores unparseable files